review_data.title: Large flavorful Fajita, quick service, outside seating
review_data.content: Located in the middle of old town, it is a nice place to grab a quick bite and beer. They have freshly prepared Fajitas served scorching hot and go well with cold local draft beer. While walking in the Aldstadt and craving for spicy food,...More
